          <br>
          <p>Check the sidebar to see what's popular. Check below for your interest feed.</p>
        </header>
        <main class="bg-indigo-300 rounded-lg drop-shadow-xl p-8 mt-8">
          test
        </main>
      </div>
      <div class="basis-1/3">
        <aside class="bg-indigo-300 rounded-lg drop-shadow-xl p-8">
          <input type="text" placeholder="ðŸ” Search..." class="bg-indigo-200 rounded-full w-full mb-4 p-1/4 drop-shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-xl"><i>Trending interests</i></h2>
          <p id="popular"><%= trending %></p>
        </aside>
        <br>
        <footer class="text-xs text-center">ExSemantica v<%= Application.spec(:exsemantica, :vsn) %> with IndigoChild theme - <a href="https://github.com/Chlorophytus/exsemantica" class="underline decoration-sky-600 text-sky-600">Fork me on GitHub!</a></footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
